metadata.name: Ticket #1 for the Non Fungible Conference 2023
metadata.description: Access to the Non-Fungible Conference on June 7th & 8th, 2023 from 9am-6pm on both days. This ArtWork is the first collaboration between @CarlosMarcialt and @Coldie. Thanks to @Basileus, @CultCryptoArt who are co-editing the conference. Please Follow @NFCSummit before the conference to get instruction about how to redeem your ticket.
